        public static final int AppTheme_levelup_code_view_style

        This symbol is the offset where the R.attr.levelup_code_view_style attribute's value can be found in the AppTheme array.

        Must be a reference to another resource, in the form "@[+][package:]type:name" or to a theme attribute in the form "?[package:][type:]name".
